        "text_ftwgeF": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Named after our founder Gillian Crawford's grandmother, Lily Blanche is built on a foundation of creativity and meticulous craftsmanship. Every single piece that we create is designed to tell a story-your story- with profound sentiment. We are dedicated to creating the heirlooms of tomorrow from the conversation of pieces today, ensuring that our jewellery becomes a precious part of your legacy. </p>"
