          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Free Photo Service",
            "text": "<p>We offer a complimentary photo service with all of our lockets, ensuring that your memories are perfectly preserved within your chosen piece. Our personalisation experts ensure optimal image quality and placement.</p>",
