    "rich_text_6wDLVU": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_yLYayx": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Ethical & Sustainable Practices: A Lighter Footprint",
            "heading_size": "h1",
            "heading_tag": "h3"
          }
        },
        "text_3VK4cF": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We are deeply committed to minimizing our environmental impact and fostering a responsible business. Our sustainability plan outlines our dedication to creating jewellery that is beautiful both in design and in its impact on our planet.</p><p></p><h3><strong>Net Zero Commitment by 2050</strong></h3><p>Wow (Scotland) Ltd, the parent company of Lily Blanche, is committed to achieving net zero status by 2050. We are actively working to ensure our footprint is as light as possible while still creating jobs, growing the economy, and servicing our customers with excellence.</p><p></p><h3><strong>Love Local & Ethical Supply Chain</strong></h3><p>We prioritize working with UK suppliers and maintain personal relationships throughout our supply chain, from printers to gem-cutters, emphasizing ethical business practices. We also carry out repairs locally to reduce our carbon footprint. By keeping our operations close to home, we support the local economy while minimizing transportation emissions.</p><h3><strong>Sustainable Packaging Solutions</strong></h3><p>Our packaging boxes are sourced from a UK supplier and are fully biodegradable, reusable, and recyclable, made from 75% recycled material. We offer a \"go paperless\" option at checkout to further reduce waste. Our packaging supplier uses only ethically sourced raw materials, and their pulp and board suppliers are FSC accredited with re-afforestation programmes.</p><h3><strong>Carbon Offsetting & Green Partnerships</strong></h3><p>We partner with More Trees to help offset our carbon footprint and utilize delivery partners like Royal Mail, who are leading the way in the move to net zero with all-electric vehicle hubs. We are committed to making sustainable choices at every stage of our business operations.</p>"
          }
        },
        "button_Pi7i6G": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
            "button_label": "Read More About Our Sustainability Promise Here",
            "button_link": "https://www.lilyblanche.com/pages/sustainability-plan",
            "button_style_secondary": false,
            "button_label_2": "",
            "button_link_2": "",
            "button_style_secondary_2": false
          }
        }
      },
